-- Sierra Leone Says Vodacom Interested in Telecoms Investment
-- B y   S i l a s   G b a n d i a
-- 2012-06-04T15:37:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-04/sierra-leone-says-vodacom-interested-in-telecoms-investment.html
Vodacom Group Ltd. (VOD)  of South Africa
has expressed interest in investing in telecommunications in
 Sierra Leone , said Mohamed Bangura, director general of the
National Telecommunications Commission.  A delegation from Vodacom visited the capital, Freetown,
and met officials from the commission and the Ministry of
Information and Communications, Bangura said by phone today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Silas Gbandia in Freetown at 
 sgbandia@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Emily Bowers at 
 ebowers1@bloomberg.net  